Interface Yutsis

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Graph
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractYutsis
public interface Yutsis
extends Graph

Interface of a (cubic) graph allowing the graph transformations used to reduce a Yutsis graph.

Dries.VanDyck@rug.ac.be
